Say '''Butig''' et kumanem ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Lanao del Sur]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 16,642 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 331.49 sq. km. Sikato et walad kumadwa ya distrito. Say zip code to et 9305.	
															
